    bibo:volume "1466" ;
    dc:creator "Afonso-Dias, Isabel; Kalavati, Chaganti; Mackenzie, Ken; Mackenzie, Kevin S." ;
    dc:date "2007" ;
    dc:title "Three new species of Myxosporea (Bivalvulida: Ceratomyxidae: Alatasporidae) from the gall bladders of anglerfishes Lophius spp. (Teleostei: Lophiidae) in the Northeast Atlantic Ocean" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176576> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176576>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 15. Pseudalataspora lophii n. sp. 10. Young trophozoite with non-bifurcated tip, unstained fixed specimen. 11. Trophozoite with developing spores and bifurcated tip, unstained fixed specimen. 12. Spore, sutural view, stained with Giemsa. 13. Spore, sutural view, unstained fixed specimen. 14. Spore, polar view, stained with Giemsa. Scale-bars: 10 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176576/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

